schedule.title: Kickoff Ceremony
schedule.desc: Come out to our opening ceremony to learn about the schedule, rules, and resources for WebJam! We will also be going over all of the exciting workshops we have planned for the week, so make sure to come by to learn more.

schedule.title: Peter teaches Petr-making
schedule.desc: Did you know that the Design at UCI logo is actually an Anteater? Crazy, right? If you can't see it, the dot is its eye, and it's looking upwards and to the right!
